    "long_instructions": "## Solving a Riddle\r\nBased on this flowchart logic, add to the start code to complete the program. \r\n- If the riddle is solved correctly, print \"You move forward.\"\r\n- If incorrect, ask if they want a hint:\r\n    - \"yes\" → Give hint.\r\n    - \"no\" → Print \"Try again.\"",
